
Unreleased
 - Name is now required for all port assignments
 - Enforce unique name per project_dir (duplicate names in the same project are rejected)
 - Added `edit-as-text` CLI command to edit all assignments in your text editor
 - Added `updateAssignment()`, `serializeAssignments()`, `parseAssignmentText()`, and `applyAssignmentEdits()` functions

0.4.0
 - Switch from better-sqlite3 to node:sqlite via userdata-db 0.2.0

0.3.0
 - Added `get-or-claim` CLI command (idempotent port assignment by name)

0.2.0
 - Added project_dir column to track which project claimed each port
 - `list` now filters by current project directory (use `--project-dir` to override)
 - Added `list-all` command to show ports across all projects
 - Replaced `--cwd` CLI option with `--project-dir`
 - Added `getOrClaimPort()` - looks up existing port by project_dir + name, or claims a new one
 - Added `getPortByName()` - looks up a port assignment by project_dir + name

0.1.1
 - Fix broken package.json deps

0.1.0
 - Initial release
